Description: Automated LaTeX article generation with modern CLI
 Rxiv-Maker is a comprehensive tool for automated LaTeX article generation
 with modern CLI and figure creation capabilities. It streamlines the process
 of creating scientific manuscripts by:
 .
  * Converting Markdown to LaTeX with advanced formatting
  * Automatic figure generation from Python/R scripts
  * DOI validation and bibliography management
  * Cross-platform compatibility (Docker/Podman support)
  * Modern CLI with rich output formatting
  * Comprehensive validation and error handling
 .
 The tool supports multiple workflows including local development,
 containerized execution, and integration with CI/CD pipelines.
 Perfect for researchers, academics, and anyone who needs to generate
 high-quality scientific documents efficiently.

